data.description: This amazing Home just Hit the Market at an Extremely Low Price and is being Sold As Is!  It is ready for creative minds to put their thinking caps and create the perfect space for your family! As you walk in, you will find one of two spacious Living Areas downstairs, where one of them can become an Office, Formal Dining, or Welcome Area and the other becomes your grand living room which flows into the kitchen space for great entertainment and conversation to have with loved ones. The kitchen has plenty of storage space as well as a perfect breakfast nook with windows that overlook your backyard view. As you head upstairs you enter an oversized open room that can be utilized as a game, play, or media, room! The Primary bedroom is fit for a true Texas King Bed and still have plenty of space to spare. The other two bedrooms are great in size and not your standard 10 x 10 bedrooms. So anyone staying in there would greatly appreciate the space. Last but not least, the backyard. You have a beautiful view with no backdoor neighbors just perfect Texas sky-high views. The backyard is huge and ready for you to design your dream oasis and entertainment space for family or friend gatherings. Either extend a wonderful Patio Deck to enjoy seeing more of the scenery, as you walk down some steps to a possible swimming pool and still have plenty of space for swing sets and more! Can you imagine the cookouts as you look into this relaxing nature view that will make you feel you have escaped San Antonio living even though you are minutes away from Randolph Airforce Base, Near Ft Sam, Restaurants, and Shopping. So call your favorite Realtor and see this home before it's gone and you miss another great opportunity.
